content.rendered:
Yuta Okkotsu is enrolled by the Jujutsu Witch Masters at Tokyo Prefectural Jujutsu High School to help him control his powers and keep an eye on him.

Directed By Seong-Hu Park

Written By Gege Akutami. Hiroshi Seko

Stars: Chinatsu Akasaki. Aya Endô. Kana Hanazawa
